-- Canada Appoints Sonia L’Heureux as Interim Budget Officer
-- B y   G r e g   Q u i n n
-- 2013-03-08T00:10:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-08/canada-appoints-sonia-l-heureux-as-interim-budget-officer.html
Canada named Sonia L’Heureux interim
parliamentary budget officer, Government House Leader Peter  Van
Loan  said.  L’Heureux, the parliamentary librarian, will take over from
Kevin Page when he finishes his term. Richard Fujarczuk becomes
Law Clerk and Parliamentary Counsel of the House of Commons, Van
Loan said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Greg Quinn in Ottawa at 
